01:24:55,195 --> 01:24:55,904
Sedi

820
01:25:03,622 --> 01:25:04,580
Popij to

821
01:25:09,253 --> 01:25:10,295
lskapi

822
01:25:10,797 --> 01:25:12,632
Tako je medicinski

823
01:25:19,807 --> 01:25:24,938
To je dobro prije rasprave o
necemu za cim srce cezne

824
01:25:25,313 --> 01:25:28,441
Mislim.. Hemingway mi je to rekao...
Poznajes Ernesta Hemingwaya?

825
01:25:29,109 --> 01:25:30,652
Margot tacnije

826
01:25:33,739 --> 01:25:36,285
No ni lepota uvek ne
izbegne tragediju

827
01:25:36,618 --> 01:25:39,328
Oh Boze, ovo je pakao...

828
01:25:41,582 --> 01:25:43,125
Uradio sam nesto

829
01:25:45,003 --> 01:25:46,796
Kriv sam...

830
01:25:47,964 --> 01:25:49,633
l ispastacu zbog toga.

831
01:25:52,802 --> 01:25:59,311
Zanimljivo o krivici... nista nije
toliko lose da malo tvoje krivnjr
to moze pogorsati jos vise

832
01:25:59,978 --> 01:26:04,774
i nista nije toliko dobro da
krivnja ne moze poboljsati

833
01:26:05,442 --> 01:26:10,657
Krivnja nam skrece paznju s istine...
mi imamo sposobnosti zaceljivanja

834
01:26:14,036 --> 01:26:19,375
Nastavljamo ziveti cak i
sa slomljenim srcem

835
01:26:21,336 --> 01:26:22,629
Kako?

836
01:26:25,799 --> 01:26:27,801
Vezbom

837
01:26:45,864 --> 01:26:49,034
3 sata... pizdo

838
01:26:49,452 --> 01:26:55,333
Radila sam u studiju..nisam mogla
napraviti pesmu za singl

839
01:26:55,667 --> 01:26:58,504
A ti?Nisam mogao zaspati.

840
01:26:59,171 --> 01:27:01,840
l... onda sedis u mraku?

841
01:27:02,675 --> 01:27:09,516
Hej, hajde da odjebemo lose misli
i da se sabijemo od palacinki, ha?

842
01:27:12,019 --> 01:27:16,691
Da... lpak mislim da cu u krevet

843
01:27:49,020 --> 01:27:53,024
Netvrtak, 3 ujutro, opet ne
mogu da zaspim

844
01:27:53,357 --> 01:27:58,531
Kao da cekam da se deo mene popravi
a on je i dalje razbijen

845
01:27:58,865 --> 01:28:03,202
Vec sam podelio novine i oprao
prljavo supe

846
01:28:03,703 --> 01:28:08,709
nista ne radim nego sedim
ovde i cekam

847
01:28:09,084 --> 01:28:14,048
Kao grapanin i birac U LA
sto zavisi od vas

848
01:28:14,131 --> 01:28:15,842
ako dopustite...

849
01:28:33,696 --> 01:28:35,740
Di ces s mojim cvecem

850
01:28:36,407 --> 01:28:41,538
Paaa vidis da je...Mi ne bacamo
nista sto nije skroz mrtvo

851
01:28:43,123 --> 01:28:44,875
Vazi?

852
01:28:46,962 --> 01:28:52,550
l jos nesto...Otkako si dosao
sazaljevas se.To me deprimira

853
01:28:56,889 --> 01:28:59,059
Deprimiram te?

854
01:28:59,393 --> 01:29:03,563
To sam rekao.Ako smo dosli dotle da
razvlacis dan kod mene...

855
01:29:03,981 --> 01:29:09,153
onda imamo problem...ozbiljno

856
01:29:09,570 --> 01:29:13,658
moras uraditi nesto...
vreme je da snimis film.

857
01:29:17,538 --> 01:29:19,541
Napi put da propes kroz ovo

858
01:29:20,458 --> 01:29:22,919
Jesi li prorok sada?

859
01:29:25,547 --> 01:29:30,428
Nah... Samo sam ti prijatelj

860
01:30:15,563 --> 01:30:19,442
Zdravo, mogu li ti pomoci?
Jeste li vi mama Arona Davisa?

861
01:30:19,777 --> 01:30:21,445
Ja sam sestra Davis da

862
01:30:21,654 --> 01:30:23,948
Poznavao sam vaseg sina,
u Los Angeles

863
01:30:24,490 --> 01:30:28,787
Vi mora da ste neki od staresina
tamo cim tako izgledate

864
01:30:29,120 --> 01:30:31,957
Ne, moje ime jeristian

865
01:30:34,460 --> 01:30:36,086
lzgubio je svoj sat

866
01:30:39,590 --> 01:30:42,344
zelim da znate koliko mi je zao

867
01:30:43,845 --> 01:30:48,183
Ubija me pomisao da sam mu
naneo bilo kakvu bol

868
01:31:17,092 --> 01:31:19,762
Nekaj!

869
01:33:18,315 --> 01:33:20,860
Moglo je biti i gore...
moglo je kisiti

870
01:33:21,276 --> 01:33:25,072
Oh jelda... pa pada kisa

871
01:33:25,656 --> 01:33:28,994
Samo u LA zaista pada kisa
kad najave na TV

872
01:33:30,329 --> 01:33:33,123
Mislis li da ima mojih
racuna u toj posti

873
01:33:42,593 --> 01:33:46,055
Oh boze...kopija mog videa..

874
01:33:46,347 --> 01:33:47,681
Sta?

875
01:33:48,349 --> 01:33:50,727
Ma daj... to je zbog loseg vremena

876
01:33:51,061 --> 01:33:53,021
Jedva cekam da vidim

877
01:33:53,897 --> 01:33:58,694
Hajde mala, pusti strogo poverljivo.
Pogledajmo to

878
01:34:09,206 --> 01:34:15,254
Zasto... Jel to neka kopija
Kristine Agilere,sta nije u redu?

879
01:34:16,256 --> 01:34:19,093
Ne, to je samo...

880
01:35:04,645 --> 01:35:06,647
Sta je ovo jebote...

881
01:35:09,150 --> 01:35:13,488
To je iz mog dnevnika,sta stvari
odatle rade ovde

882
01:35:13,822 --> 01:35:17,618
Uvek si mi govorio da napisem pesmu
o tebi... Htela sam ti reci...

883
01:35:17,827 --> 01:35:21,748
ili te pitati ili bilo sta drugo...
Znala si da cu ti reci da se jebes..

884
01:35:22,165 --> 01:35:26,754
Pa sta si uradila?Ukrala si moje
najprivatnije stvari,koje sam hteo

885
01:35:27,379 --> 01:35:29,799
ostaviti iza sebe,a ti si
mi ih bacila u lice?

886
01:35:30,008 --> 01:35:32,259
Mislila sam da ce nesto
dobro izaci iz ovoga.

887
01:35:32,634 --> 01:35:33,720
Oh za tebe mozda...

888
01:35:34,054 --> 01:35:36,556
lsuse Kriste...Htela sam ti reci.

889
01:35:37,475 --> 01:35:43,731
Slusaj...Nisam ti htela reci ovako...
Li producenti ploce...

890
01:35:44,065 --> 01:35:46,902
zele da se preselim
u New York na neko vreme.

891
01:35:47,194 --> 01:35:50,698
Zato sto... sto svi dobri
producenti rade tamo

892
01:35:53,201 --> 01:35:57,372
Nek ti je sa srecom.

893
01:37:00,319 --> 01:37:01,362
lzvoli?

894
01:37:01,654 --> 01:37:07,911
Trazim Kristian...
Da um... Ne Kris je um....

895
01:37:08,829 --> 01:37:11,833
zelis li da mu ostavis neku poruku
ili nesto drugo?

896
01:37:27,851 --> 01:37:29,103
cuo sam da nisi dobila deonice

897
01:37:29,561 --> 01:37:32,898
Mrzim priznati ali nedostajaces
mi kad odes u Njujork

898
01:37:33,190 --> 01:37:34,567
Ko ti je rekao da odlazim

899
01:37:34,859 --> 01:37:36,069
Ma daj, pa ti mrzis LA

900
01:37:37,529 --> 01:37:41,033
Ako kazes nekom sta sam ti rekla
zasit cu ti usne

901
01:37:42,618 --> 01:37:44,453
Bila sam nesretna u Njujorku

902
01:37:45,120 --> 01:37:49,042
U LA mozes biti nesretan
jedino kad preplanes

903
01:38:10,900 --> 01:38:12,444
Moj dragi decko

904
01:38:17,908 --> 01:38:21,204
Naravno da vredi

905
01:38:22,872 --> 01:38:25,876
Nisam imao ni jedno drugo
mesto gde bih otisao

906
01:38:27,878 --> 01:38:29,505
Dobrodosao

907
01:38:32,717 --> 01:38:34,720
Daj mom mladom prijatelju
sta god hoce

908
01:38:35,637 --> 01:38:38,683
lzvoli...
Samo kolu, hvala

909
01:38:39,183 --> 01:38:41,143
Nista jace?

910
01:38:41,601 --> 01:38:43,187
lzgledas kao da bi ti koristilo

911
01:38:43,646 --> 01:38:46,650
Ako ne smeta rekla bi da izgledas
nekako uh mmm....pakleno?

912
01:38:47,276 --> 01:38:48,277
Zasto?

913
01:38:49,445 --> 01:38:51,114
Nisam dosao ovde da te opterecujem

914
01:38:51,406 --> 01:38:55,118
Pa, ti si meni dao tu privilegiju
dozvoli da i ja tebi uzvratim

915
01:38:58,580 --> 01:39:04,670
Nakon sto smo se sreli bio sam
poslan kuci i izbacen

916
01:39:06,088 --> 01:39:08,175
zato sto sam postao peder

917
01:39:09,384 --> 01:39:12,847
Tvoja crkva ne voli alkohol
i homoseksualce

918
01:39:13,806 --> 01:39:16,601
Skroz sam zaprepastena ne mogu

919
01:39:18,603 --> 01:39:21,565
zamisliti raj bez oboje

920
01:39:21,815 --> 01:39:23,233
lzvini, nastavi

921
01:39:25,403 --> 01:39:32,660
To me je dovelo do toga da se
pokusam ubiti

922
01:39:45,634 --> 01:39:47,637
Nakon sto su me zakrpali u bolnici

923
01:39:49,055 --> 01:39:53,226
roditelji su me poslali na
to mesto

924
01:39:54,519 --> 01:39:57,773
gde su me u stvari trebali
promeniti

925
01:39:59,442 --> 01:40:00,860
i popraviti me

926
01:40:01,444 --> 01:40:04,447
jedne veceri kad sam bio na
rekonstrukciji

927
01:40:05,031 --> 01:40:09,203
i kad sam cistio pod cetkom

928
01:40:09,620 --> 01:40:11,205
tad sam cuo to

929
01:40:11,872 --> 01:40:13,291
taj glas

930
01:40:15,543 --> 01:40:16,837
bio je anpeoski

931
01:40:29,268 --> 01:40:31,729
To je bio samo TV

932
01:40:35,233 --> 01:40:37,444
Bila je to samo cudna slucajnost

933
01:40:39,279 --> 01:40:41,197
Ja ne verujem u slucajnosti

934
01:40:41,740 --> 01:40:44,201
mislim da se tad desilo cudo

935
01:40:45,369 --> 01:40:46,705
Mozda

936
01:40:48,415 --> 01:40:51,418
Zato sto devojka koja je pevala

937
01:40:52,878 --> 01:40:55,048
je poznata a ja sam je poznavao

938
01:40:56,257 --> 01:40:58,092
jesam

939
01:41:00,012 --> 01:41:03,389
Znam sta ljudi osecaju kad
cuju takve pesme

940
01:41:07,144 --> 01:41:09,814
ali ja sam osetio da je
ova pesma bila upucena meni

941
01:41:17,114 --> 01:41:18,616
Ovo je moj mladi prijatelj

942
01:41:18,949 --> 01:41:20,117
Znamo se

943
01:41:20,911 --> 01:41:22,287
Bio sam kod tebe...
lznajmio sam ga...

944
01:41:23,246 --> 01:41:24,831
Jel to, ne nije moguce...

945
01:41:38,764 --> 01:41:41,183
On ostavlja odlicne napojnice

946
01:41:51,695 --> 01:41:54,657
Draga hrana ce se oladiti

947
01:41:54,657 --> 01:41:56,535
Nosim vruce!

948
01:42:15,222 --> 01:42:16,473
Zdravica

949
01:42:18,059 --> 01:42:19,477
Jednu tvrdnju

950
01:42:20,645 --> 01:42:22,732
l molitvu zahvale

951
01:42:24,233 --> 01:42:28,738
zelim da znate gde god da se
napemo u svetu

952
01:42:29,906 --> 01:42:32,409
koliki god bili nasi uspesi
ili padovi

953
01:42:32,909 --> 01:42:36,706
uvek cete imati mesta
za mojim stolom...

954
01:42:37,873 --> 01:42:39,709
i u mom srcu

955
01:42:57,980 --> 01:43:01,317
Ponekad to izgleda
kao gomila tacaka

956
01:43:02,526 --> 01:43:03,527
ali

957
01:43:04,321 --> 01:43:05,072
sve vise i vise

958
01:43:06,406 --> 01:43:08,409
osecam kao da smo svi
mi povezani

959
01:43:09,535 --> 01:43:11,412
i osecam se super

960
01:43:12,038 --> 01:43:13,081
i zabavno

961
01:43:14,540 --> 01:43:17,211
i dobro.

